            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">16.307</ph> Contract clauses.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d993e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1007e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            
					          </p>
					          <ol id="d993e23" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1007e27" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1058307.dita#i1058307"
                              base="i1058307"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.216-7</xref>, Allowable Cost and Payment, in solicitations and contracts when a cost-reimbursement contract or a time-and-materials contract (other than a contract for a commercial item) is contemplated. If the contract is a time-and-materials contract, the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1058307.dita#i1058307"
                              base="i1058307"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.216-7</xref> applies in conjunction with the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1049486.dita#i1049486"
                              base="i1049486"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.232-7</xref>), but only to the portion of the contract that provides for reimbursement of materials (as defined in the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1049486.dita#i1049486"
                              base="i1049486"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.232-7</xref>) at actual cost. Further, the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1058307.dita#i1058307"
                              base="i1058307"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.216-7</xref> does not apply to labor-hour contracts.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1007e52" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                If the contract is a construction contract and contains the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1050318.dita#i1050318"
                              base="i1050318"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.232-27</xref>, Prompt Payment for Construction Contracts, the contracting officer shall use the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1058307.dita#i1058307"
                              base="i1058307"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.216-7</xref> with its Alternate I.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1007e67" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                If the contract is with an educational institution, the contracting officer shall use the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1058307.dita#i1058307"
                              base="i1058307"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.216-7</xref> with its Alternate II.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1007e79" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                If the contract is with a State or local government, the contracting officer shall use the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1058307.dita#i1058307"
                              base="i1058307"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.216-7</xref> with its Alternate III.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1007e91" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(5)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                If the contract is with a nonprofit organization other than an educational institution, a State or local government, or a nonprofit organization exempted under the OMB Uniform Guidance at 2 CFR part 200, appendix VIII, the contracting officer shall use the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1058307.dita#i1058307"
                              base="i1058307"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.216-7</xref> with its Alternate IV.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1007e105" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1058442.dita#i1058442"
                        base="i1058442"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.216-8</xref>, Fixed Fee, in solicitations and contracts when a cost-plus-fixed-fee contract (other than a construction contract) is contemplated.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1007e117" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1058452.dita#i1058452"
                        base="i1058452"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.216-9</xref>, Fixed-Fee-Construction, in solicitations and contracts when a cost-plus-fixed-fee construction contract is contemplated.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1007e129" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1058463.dita#i1058463"
                        base="i1058463"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.216-10</xref>, Incentive Fee, in solicitations and contracts when a cost-plus-incentive-fee contract is contemplated.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1007e141" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            
					          </p>
					          <ol id="d993e147" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1007e151" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1058495.dita#i1058495"
                              base="i1058495"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.216-11</xref>, Cost Contract-No Fee, in solicitations and contracts when a cost-reimbursement contract is contemplated that provides no fee and is not a cost-sharing contract.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1007e163" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                If a cost-reimbursement research and development contract with an educational institution or a nonprofit organization that provides no fee or other payment above cost and is not a cost-sharing contract is contemplated, and if the contracting officer determines that withholding of a portion of allowable costs is not required, the contracting officer shall use the clause with its Alternate I.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1007e175" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(f)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            
					          </p>
					          <ol id="d993e181" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1007e185" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1058506.dita#i1058506"
                              base="i1058506"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.216-12</xref>, Cost-Sharing Contract-No Fee, in solicitations and contracts when a cost-sharing contract is contemplated.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1007e197" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                If a cost-sharing research and development contract with an educational institution or a nonprofit organization is contemplated, and if the contracting officer determines that withholding of a portion of allowable costs is not required, the contracting officer shall use the clause with its Alternate I.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1007e208" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(g)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1058519.dita#i1058519"
                        base="i1058519"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.216-15</xref>, Predetermined Indirect Cost Rates, in solicitations and contracts when a cost-reimbursement research and development contract with an educational institution (see <xref href="FAR-i1075270.dita#i1075270"
                        base="i1075270"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">42.705-3</xref>(b)) is contemplated and predetermined indirect cost rates are to be used.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
		    </conbody>
